
ensure that UFW is installed and enabled:
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install ufw
sudo ufw enable



sudo ufw status verbose



sudo ufw status



sudo ufw enable



sudo ufw default deny incoming



Allow incoming traffic from the specific network (192.168.0.0/24) on ports 80, 443, and 9443
sudo ufw allow from 192.168.0.0/24 to any port 80
sudo ufw allow from 192.168.0.0/24 to any port 443
sudo ufw allow from 192.168.0.0/24 to any port 9443




Allow incoming traffic from the specific IP address on any port:
sudo ufw allow from your_ip_address
